health_test.testShortDescription: Check if TSO (TCP Segmentation Offload) is enabled for pNIC. TSO on the transmission path of physical network adapters improves the performance of ESXi hosts by reducing the overhead of the CPU for TCP/IP network operations. When TSO is enabled, the network adapter divides larger data chunks into TCP segments instead of the CPU.
